s(\"unchecked\")\n        ProducerRecord<String, String> record = Utils.newParameterizedInstance(\n                ProducerRecord.class.getName(),\n                String.class,\n                \"utils-topic\",\n                Object.class,\n                \"record-value\");\n\n        assertEquals(\"utils-topic\", record.topic());\n        assertEquals(\"record-value\", record.value());\n        assertNull(record.key());\n        assertNull(record.partition());\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    void reportsAbstractKafkaSubclasses() {\n        ConfigException exception = assertThrows(\n                ConfigException.class,\n                () -> Utils.ensureConcreteSubclass(TopicCollection.class, TopicCollection.class));\n\n        assertTrue(exception.getMessage().contains(\"This class is abstract and cannot be created.\"));\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 547, "output": 702, "cacheRead": 31744, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 32993, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777514488185, "responseId": "resp_0c3324abf89a3b5f0169f2b7f8aba881a186ac3ac1f4ee2964"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_FbaqjQZ3H4NhwrUZ5FwHoIhI|fc_0c3324abf89a3b5f0169f2b7fbe12881a1bcbf25a264464637", "toolName": "write", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully wrote 2297 bytes to tests/src/org.apache.kafka/kafka-clients/4.2.0/src/test/java/org_apache_kafka/kafka_clients/UtilsTest.java"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777514495077}]}
